{"tid":1789123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 死亡九巴：慘劇增至19死63傷　重案探員到場蒐證","createTime":"2019-12-19T08:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T08:53:14.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b584e483bb3f27ef40f280fd30aa875c7b4d38","tid":1789123,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180211/photo/bkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180211092151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180211%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180211092151&h=b8404020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【07:45】10多重案組探員到大埔公路現場調查，探員在日光下再仔細搜索，在山邊檢獲一部手機及染血100元紙幣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180211/photo/bkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_06b.jpg?20180211092151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180211%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20180211092151&h=5063bb58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【04:53】當局再修正，聯合醫院一名傷勢危殆男子，於今晨4時34分不治，死亡人數增加至19人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180211/photo/bkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_07b.jpg?20180211092151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180211%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20180211092151&h=d146de7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【04:48】肇事九巴被拖往大欖汽車扣留中心等候查驗，現場大批機動部隊警員隨即一字<br />\n排開，在場協助搜證。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180211/photo/bkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_08b.jpg?20180211092151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180211%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20180211092151&h=3253d5b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【04:10】今晨3時許，當局修正死亡人數為18人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180211/photo/bkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_09b.jpg?20180211092151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180211%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_09b.jpg%3F20180211092151&h=b376b091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【01:00】聯合醫院一名危殆男傷者不治，死亡人數增至19人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180211/photo/bkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_11b.jpg?20180211092151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180211%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_11b.jpg%3F20180211092151&h=c4f01c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴大埔公路掟彎「舞龍」翻側，釀至少18死64傷慘劇。滿載散場馬迷的特別線九巴，昨日(2月10日)傍晚6時15分，沿大埔公路駛向大埔市中心，途經樟樹灘與松仔園之間一個右彎時失控，在路面留下50米胎痕，繼而剷平巴士站復向左翻側，多人被拋出及壓在車底，巴士內外「人疊人」「屍疊屍」，輕傷者破窗逃命，消防員救出至少24名被困乘客，證實18人當場死亡，64名傷者中有10人命危，料死亡人數會上升，肇禍的兼職九巴車長涉嫌危駕引致他人死亡被捕，有傷者指巴士似「舞龍咁舞」及入彎無收油。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180211/photo/bkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_12b.jpg?20180211092151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180211%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_12b.jpg%3F20180211092151&h=9ceeb509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當場死亡的18人中，包括14男4女，遺體昨晚深夜由現場移送到多間醫院殮房。據悉，64名傷者被分別送往11間醫院救治，暫時有9男1女情況危殆，20人情況嚴重。醫管局啓動重大事故應變機制，調動人員參與搶救。這宗在農曆新年前的災難，至少拆散18個家庭，大批家屬深夜趕到現場和醫院打聽家人下落，部分人得知家人遇難，悲痛欲絕。警方設立查詢熱線方便死傷者家屬查詢親人所在的醫院，當局又在各醫院設立跨部門援助站，向死傷者家人提供協助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180211/photo/bkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180211092151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180211%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180211013931752-0211_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180211092151&h=617b8c2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f46f55a99d50f5013039f3d994c76260696f4ea5","tid":1789123,"uid":9356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"屌你回帶做乜尻<br />\n一開連登即見到突然咁多不治<br />\n即開蘋果睇<br />\n又唔見有報<br />\n<br />\n返返黎先見到回帶兩隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea103f271d23739865f7583ef934a0c7d85ce44","tid":1789123,"uid":269481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"仆你臭街，好好玩咩？冚家鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}